{"4260530": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "列車安全搜查官梨奈", "steam_appid": 4260530, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4260530/extras/e0aabd33ad46e1bd801ab524d1c1fc11.poster.avif?t=1771607669\" width=780 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4260530/extras/e0aabd33ad46e1bd801ab524d1c1fc11.webm?t=1771607669\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4260530/extras/e0aabd33ad46e1bd801ab524d1c1fc11.mp4?t=1771607669\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4260530/extras/16049943f4b9a1fbeb1b394e1a2c25ca.avif?t=1771607669\" width=780 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隨著列車裡的犯罪率不斷攀升，警察啟動了名為列車臥底作戰的特殊行動。於是，一支由具備超能力的列車調查員所組成的全新調查單位由此成立。然而，主力調查員莉娜在行動中被以海鬥為首的犯罪團夥給抓住了，她也因此失去了自己的能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但這並沒有讓她退縮。失去能力的莉娜究竟還能不能恢復能力還有逮捕海鬥和他的同夥呢？又或者，她會在失敗後被迫放棄調查員的身份呢？ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4260530/extras/4fb8baddabbc6af151f86dd29cc2fa3a.avif?t=1771607669\" width=780 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在這款肉鴿遊戲裡，你將扮演列車特殊調查員莉娜，利用超能力在列車上抓捕犯罪分子。戰鬥過程中需要精準把控技能釋放的時機，同時應對敵人的行動。你可以使用預見技能來預測未來用以躲避攻擊，用電擊技能控住敵人，再用暴風雪技能把敵人原地冰封。開啟警戒技能來發現並逮捕罪犯吧！透過抓捕敵人來獲得經驗、升級、自由選擇強化方向。每個車站都會觸發隨機事件，這些事件有可能會帶來幫助，也可能會添堵。每場任務的關底都將迎來一場獨特的Boss戰。靈活制定戰術、購買強化、抓捕罪犯、盡情享受遊戲的樂趣吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4260530/extras/245d384ea34ccbdf2a3d88d343165d0f.poster.avif?t=1771607669\" width=780 height=608 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4260530/extras/245d384ea34ccbdf2a3d88d343165d0f.webm?t=1771607669\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4260530/extras/245d384ea34ccbdf2a3d88d343165d0f.mp4?t=1771607669\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4260530/extras/74d30d9fbd32863b463d5a45cac668e7.avif?t=1771607669\" width=780 height=120 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>肉鴿成長機制</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次升級時都能選擇想要的技能。即使輸了，也能用在任務中獲得的技能點數來解鎖升級。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>特殊Boss戰</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次任務都會遇到不同的Boss，你需要將其擊敗並逮捕他們。他們都擁有獨特的能力，需要用不同的戰術才能贏球。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>快節奏的回合製戰術玩法！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在每個回合裡你都需要合理規劃自己的行動，同時留意敵人的行動方式。哪怕在敵人的回合裡也可以用自己的被動技能哦！記得留意計時器，在最合適的時機釋放技能吧！ </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>多套服裝</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >給莉娜買不同的衣服出任務吧，每套衣服都會有不同的加成哦！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4260530/extras/e0aabd33ad46e1bd801ab524d1c1fc11.poster.avif?t=1771607669\" width=780 height=300 ><source s