rong> Intel Core2 Duo or better<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 2 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 1 GB 可用空間</li></ul>"}, "mac_requirements": [], "linux_requirements": [], "legal_notice": "2025 Saikey Studios", "release_date": {"coming_soon": true, "date": "即將推出"}}}}